beer.beer_description:
Hops: Citra, Nelson Sauvin, Hersbruker, Yakima Valley.

An approachable but flavoursome beer with passionfruit and citrus aromas, thanks to a unique combination of hops added to the brew - including our signature hop from the Yakima Valley at the foothills of the Cascade Mountain Range.
